name: Timothy James
summary: Versatile Australian actor and tenor with 15+ years' professional experience across film, television, musical theatre, commercial and corporate projects in Australia, the UK and the US. Screen credits include Guardians of the Galaxy, Star Wars: Rogue One and BBC's Call the Midwife; stage highlights include Les Miserables, Seussical and Next to Normal. Known for an engaging stage presence, strong comic timing and a wide vocal range (tenor). Fluent in English and conversational Japanese, with a repertoire of Australian, RP, Cockney and Standard American accents.
